nt\u1ee5ziaka set: Nchịkọta iwu CPU nwere ike ịghọta
debanye aha: Obere, ebe nchekwa dị oke ọsọ n'ime CPU
g\u1ee5\u1ecd naan\u1ecb ebe nchekwa: Na-echekwa ntuziaka ndị dị mkpa ka kọmputa malite
ebe nchekwa nchekwa: Ebe nchekwa pere mpe, ngwa ngwa dị nso na CPU maka ịnweta ngwa ngwa
nha okwu: Ọnụọgụ nke ibe n'ibe otu CPU nwere ike hazie otu oge
\u1ecdkp\u1ecdk\u1ecd: Usoro ebe CPU na-agbaji ntuziaka n'ime usoro iji rụọ ọrụ na ọtụtụ ndị otu oge
multiprocessing: Iji otutu CPU ma ọ bụ cores rụọ ọrụ n'otu oge
kwusi: Mgbama na-akwụsịtụ CPU nwa oge iji jikwaa mmemme
mebere ebe nchekwa: Usoro iji ohere diski ike dị ka ndọtị nke RAM
bios: Sistemụ Ntinye/Mpụta nke Basic, firmware nke na-ebido ngwaike na mmalite
i/o \u1ecdd\u1ee5 \u1ee5gb\u1ecd mmiri: Adreesị akọwapụtara na kọmpụta maka iji ngwaọrụ ndị dị n'akụkụ na-ekwurịta okwu
\u1ecdkw\u1ecd \u1ee5gb\u1ecdala ngwa\u1: Ngwanrọ na-enye ohere sistemụ arụmọrụ jikwaa ngwaọrụ
endianness: Usoro nke echekwara bytes na ebe nchekwa
netw\u1ecdk protocol: Usoro iwu na ụkpụrụ maka nkwukọrịta n'etiti ngwaọrụ
ngwugwu: Obere nkeji data ebufere na netwọkụ
raw\u1ee5ta: Ngwaọrụ na-ebugharị ngwugwu n'etiti netwọk dị iche iche
nkpuchi subnet: Eji iji chọpụta netwọk na akụkụ ndị ọbịa nke adreesị IP
topology: Nhazi ngwaọrụ na njikọ na netwọk
ihe nkesa ah\u1ecba ah\u1ecba: Nrụpụta netwọkụ ebe ndị ahịa na-arịọ akụrụngwa sitere na sava
dma: Nweta ebe nchekwa ozugbo, na-enye ngwaọrụ ohere ịnyefe data na-ejighi CPU
